parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel tank material can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, accidents, or environmental hazards.
symptoms: Strong gasoline fumes
fuel smell in the vehicle
fuel leaks from the fuel tank or filler neck
cracks in the fuel tank
corrosion and rust around the fuel filler neck area.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Fuel Filler Neck Solder Joint Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel filler neck solder joint can cause fuel leaks, which can lead to fires, accidents, or environmental hazards.
symptoms: Fuel leaks from the fuel filler neck solder joint area
corrosion and rust around the fuel filler neck area
strong gasoline fumes
fuel smell in the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate repair of the fuel tank or fuel filler neck during the recall can cause the problem to reoccur, leading to fuel leaks, fires, accidents, or environmental hazards.
symptoms: Fuel leaks or fuel smell after recall repair
corrosion and rust around the fuel filler neck area
strong gasoline fumes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag computer module can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to either unwanted airbag deployments or the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag sensor light remains on
airbags deploy unexpectedly
airbags fail to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A broken or cracked frame can compromise the structural integrity of the vehicle, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Front passenger tire wiggles or vibrates while driving
loss of control of the vehicle
difficulty opening doors due to frame movement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause a loss of stopping power, leading to accidents or near-misses, and potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Spongy brake pedal
brake pedal travels to the floor
uneven brake wear
excessive front brake wear
damaged rotors
worn-out brake pads
and uneven tire wear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause the steering wheel to come loose or detach, leading to a loss of vehicle control, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel comes off in the driver's hands
the steering column is loose
the steering wheel is difficult to turn
the steering wheel requires excessive effort to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Frame Failure due to Gearbox Pressure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The pressure from the gearbox can cause the frame to weaken and break, leading to a loss of vehicle control, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The frame is broken at the steering gear
the steering column is loose
the steering linkage and lower ball joints are worn
the steering wheel is difficult to turn.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering belt tensioner bracket can cause the steering belt to malfunction, leading to a loss of power steering assist, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering belt tensioner bracket breaks
the power steering system malfunctions.
